<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  Your help desk <%= @ticket.request_label.downcase %> for
  <strong><%= @ticket.department.department_type %></strong> has been marked as completed by support and sent for user follow-up.
</p>

<p>
  Ticket No: <strong><%= @ticket.ticket_reference %></strong>
</p>

<p>
  Requester: <strong><%= @ticket.requester_name %></strong><br>
  <% if @ticket.assisted_request? && @ticket.submitted_by_user.present? %>
    Submitted by: <strong><%= @ticket.submitted_by_user.display_name %></strong> on behalf of the requester<br>
  <% end %>
  Completed by: <strong><%= @ticket.responded_by_user&.display_name || "Support Team" %></strong><br>
  Action requested from: <strong><%= @ticket.approval_pending_user&.display_name || @ticket.requester_name %></strong>
</p>

<p>
  Response:<br>
  <%= simple_format(@ticket.response_message) %>
</p>

<p>
  If the issue is still not solved, reopen this ticket with a remark. If everything is fine, close it from your side within 24 hours.
  If you take no action, the ticket will close automatically after 24 hours.
</p>
